sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as Agent Console
  participant ConsoleGW as console namespace
  participant Observer as ConsoleLiveObserverService
  participant AM as agent-manager agents

  UI->>ConsoleGW: setClient clientId
  ConsoleGW->>Observer: ensureObserving
  Observer->>AM: headless login per environment
  AM-->>Observer: chatMessage / chatEvent
  Observer->>ConsoleGW: environmentStateUpsert
  ConsoleGW-->>UI: environmentStateUpsert
